":244,"handnote":250},"ISic003280. Fragment of an Epitaph","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al0a-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α̣Ζ\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"μετὰ\">μ]ετὰ\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"τὴν\">τ̣[ὴν?]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ὑπατείαν\">[ὑπατείαν?]\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al0b-interpretive\">[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al0a-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>].Ζ\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"μετὰ\">.]ΕΤΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"τὴν\">.[..\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ὑπατείαν\">........]\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al0b-diplomatic\">[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003280_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003280_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003280.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003280-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 1\">line.1: \u003Cspan>The first letter at l. 1 could be also a Λ (according to Korhonen) or a Χ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 2\">line.2: \u003Cspan>The last letter could be also a Z or a Ξ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>… after the consulship of …\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>… dopo il consolato di …\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The fragment probably belongs to an epitaph. Korhonen restores a post-consular date: if the integration is correct and the text should not be intended as written in Latin, the inscription should be dated to the 5th century AD. For other post-consular dates in inscriptions from Catania dated to the 5th cent. AD and expressed with the formula \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">μετὰ τὴν ὑπατείαν\u003C/span>, see IG 14.455 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001279\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001279\u003C/a>, IMusCatania 167 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001648\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001648\u003C/a>, SEG 17.441 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic003126\" target=\"_blank\">ISic003126\u003C/a>.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 54.0920 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 170 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>A with serif and straight bar, squared Ε.\u003C/p> Lines 1-2  28  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[208,211,214,217,220,222,225,228,231],{"id":209,"html":210},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al0a-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α̣Ζ\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cs